title: How much does a website or branding cost?
content: The cost is calculated individually and depends on the project's objectives.

title: How long does development take?
content: On average, 2 to 6 weeks, depending on complexity.

title: How many revisions are included?
content: We provide up to 2-3 rounds of revisions at each stage.

title: Can I order just a logo or a website without branding?
content: Yes, we work on both comprehensive and individual tasks.

title: Do you provide support after the project is completed?
content: Yes, we can help with updates and maintenance.
